| `ServiceNetworkingBasic` | `tests/Samples/Sample1_TrafficController.cs` | `## Examples > Create a Traffic Controller` |
| `ServiceNetworkingSecurityPolicy` | `tests/Samples/Sample1_TrafficController.cs` | `## Examples > Configure a Security Policy (WAF)` |

